## Data Models

### User
`id (UUID) | telegram_id (BigInt, unique) | username | first_name | locale (ru) | free_question_used (bool) | created_at | updated_at`

### Chart
`id (UUID) | user_id (FK) | name | birth_datetime_utc | birth_datetime_original | latitude | longitude | tz_offset | early_rat (bool) | hidden_stems_school | chart_data (JSONB) | has_birth_time (bool) | created_at`

### Consultation
`id (UUID) | user_id (FK) | chart_id (FK) | topic | user_message (Text) | ai_response (Text) | model_used | prompt_tokens | completion_tokens | cost_usd | latency_ms | trace_id | created_at`

### Subscription
`id (UUID) | user_id (FK, unique) | plan (free/single/session/monthly) | status (active/expired) | questions_remaining | session_expires_at | monthly_expires_at | payment_provider | created_at`

### Event (для ректификации)
`id (UUID) | chart_id (FK) | event_date | event_type | description | created_at`

Связи: User 1→N Chart, User 1→N Consultation, User 1→1 Subscription, Chart 1→N Event, Chart 1→N Consultation

